Inferring the effects of landscape structure on roe deer movements using a step selection function

this is the link to the GME software
http://www.spatialecology.com/gme/movementssfsim1.htm
Simulates movement paths based on a step selection function (SSF) model

there is a Resource Selection Function Package (ResourceSelection) in R:
http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/ResourceSelection/ResourceSelection.pdf


